3. Hotel All Images
hotel images are groupd by captions


get hotel all images group by captioned in json format with query:


SELECT json_object_agg(
    caption, urls
) AS grouped_pictures
FROM (
    SELECT caption, json_agg(url) AS urls
    FROM public.pictures
    WHERE hotel_id = 147265
    GROUP BY caption
) AS subquery;



